reviewText: Excellent movie with innovative music! It's a tragic love story. The singing is phenomenal!!! I love this movie and it's one of the best soundtracks I've ever heard, too!
Can't say enough how much I love this movie. The brilliance of using established music along  with each actors own voice was huge in making this a one of a kind experience!
Can't put into words how much I LOVE this movie..I can watch it everyday
Id forgotten how bad the movie was. Had it had its own songwriter  and not used past artists and their music it would have earned an Academy Award that year.
